screen_desc: The screenshot displays a mobile app interface with a dark theme. It features a menu with options such as "Invoice Information," "Saved Places," "Terms and Policies," "Map Contribution," and "Support Center." A pop-up message is visible, asking the user if they really want to sign out, with "No" and "Yes" buttons for confirmation. Below the pop-up, there are additional options for changing the passcode and selecting the language, which is set to English. The app version is noted at the bottom.

ui_elements.text: Do you really want to sign out?
